- Integrated AVN 1.0 LG is developed based on Compact AVN

Information for China OPIO Platform
- 0xFC: China OPIO w/o CLU interface (most of phase1)
- 0xFD: China OPIO w/CLU interface (parts of phase1, phase2)

Information for Audio Platform Type
- 0x43 : Audio 4.0 Value";
