BA_ "GenSigSendType" SG_ 1216 HU_MON_Crc1Val 4;
BA_ "Description" SG_ 1216 HU_MON_Crc1Val "The data area for CRC calculation is based on the data length (DLC) of the message DB.
The CRC shall be calculated over the entire data block (excluding the CRC bytes) including the user data, alive counter and Data ID

